             was indicted for <rs id="t18240114-128-off718" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240114-128-off718" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240114-128-off718" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240114-128-cd719" type="crimeDate">16th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-128-off718 t18240114-128-cd719"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-128-off720 t18240114-128-cd719"></join>, a watch, value 2 l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240114-128-victim1151" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Irvine
                  <interp inst="t18240114-128-victim1151" type="surname" value="Irvine"></interp>
